The paper deals with the problem of emulating shared memory in message-passing networks, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also addresses privacy and fault-tolerance, which are topics related to cryptography (cs.CR), distributed systems (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT).
